---
layout: base.njk
title: Mind &mdash; The Margin of Education
permalink: /mind/
---
<div class="container container--narrow">
  <section class="category-intro">
    <p class="category-eyebrow">Category</p>
    <h1 class="category-headline">Mind</h1>
    <p class="category-lede">The inner work of learning. Attention, care, doubt, growth. The affective dimensions of teaching. How learners think and feel and struggle, and what teachers can do at the edges of that.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="Related publications">
    <h2 class="post-list-heading"><span>Publications</span></h2>
    <ol class="publications-list">
      <li class="publication-item">2026. Generative AI in work-integrated learning: supporting pre-service teachers' emotional labour and self-management in Australian initial teacher education. <a href="https://doi.org/10.1111/bjet.70043" target="_blank">British Journal of Educational Technology</a>.</li>
      <li class="publication-item">2025. Generative AI for supporting pre-service teachers in work-integrated learning, self-management and crisis resolution. <a href="https://doi.org/10.14742/ajet.10035" target="_blank">Australasian Journal of Educational Technology</a>.</li>
      <li class="publication-item">2025. Mentorship with ChatGPT to support self-regulated learning of pre-service teachers before and during placements. <a href="https://doi.org/10.3390/educsci15060642" target="_blank">Education Sciences</a>.</li>
    </ol>
  </section>

  <section class="post-list">
    <h2 class="post-list-heading"><span>Posts in Mind</span></h2>
    {% set postslist = collections.mind | reverse %}
    {% if postslist.length === 0 %}
      <p class="empty-state">No posts in this category yet.</p>
    {% else %}
      <ol class="posts">
        {% for post in postslist %}
          <li class="post-item">
            <a href="{{ post.url }}" class="post-link">
              <time datetime="{{ post.date | htmlDateString }}" class="post-item-date">{{ post.date | readableDate }}</time>
              <h3 class="post-item-title">{{ post.data.title }}</h3>
              {% if post.data.subtitle %}<p class="post-item-subtitle">{{ post.data.subtitle }}</p>{% endif %}
            </a>
          </li>
        {% endfor %}
      </ol>
    {% endif %}
  </section>
</div>
